      • splitLayerWithoutNsFix

        public static LayerSummary splitLayerWithoutNsFix(String fullLayerName,
                                                  boolean splitName)
                                           throws Exception
        parse full name of layer, use splitName boolean to parse layernames known to not have a service provider in the name to prevend problems with underscores in names.
      • {ns-uri}sp_layername
      • {ns-uri}layername (no service provider)
      • ns:layername (no service provider)
      • sp_ns:layername
      • sp_layername (no name space)
      • layername (no service provider and name space)
Parameters:
fullLayerName -
splitName - try to split out service provider
Returns:
Throws:
Exception

    protected final String determineFeatureTypeName(String spAbbr,
                                                String layer)
    This method determines the featureTypeName based on the given layer and prefix. Since the layer contains a {namespaceUrl} in the layer, it first needs to determine the namespace prefix. This value is saved in the featureTypeNamespacePrefix instance variable, for later use.
